{"tid":1631161,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大家知唔知點解呢幾日啲狗咁遲先出黎？","createTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T15:30:26.000Z","uid":112124,"like":16,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5e070c4b13ca457db3d7925be0def8377f52e094","tid":1631161,"uid":112124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:22.000Z","msg":"我地中撚哂計啊，林鄭要啲人同我地割席啊，所以咪比哂機會大家瘋狂破壞，要營造一個真暴徒既形象啊，你地明唔撚明啊，又話對準政權，唔該真係對準政權啊，我地咁撚樣破壞落去我地一撚定輸啊"},{"pid":"3e6575faa7b044bd91e76cc0b203cbc150dd130a","tid":1631161,"uid":112124,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"對準政權啊"},{"pid":"a4de0ba81e9c6e2fa2517c13c6087bb31443a1d7","tid":1631161,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:51:40.000Z","msg":"［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"6c47ae439aa9261da6e05b829c3ba9cae9096cd9","tid":1631161,"uid":112124,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:52:10.000Z","msg":"大家咁樣落去，已經偏離航道啦"},{"pid":"1c361a8ff247947477e8f40def08b6774db01187","tid":1631161,"uid":112124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:06.000Z","msg":"唔好沉醉左係破壞死物入面啊唔該"},{"pid":"1cc2996b1fdb9fdb82a045a6a4150aa96a811988","tid":1631161,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:10.000Z","msg":"幫手推呢個<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1630086\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1630086</a>"},{"pid":"51f344663b81d3cde7634ef07a963e9eeff12658","tid":1631161,"uid":41608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:38.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n唔好接裝修JOB!!!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MDUJOsn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDUJOsn.jpg&h=2d08b58c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c09a2143706076471d2cf728517761765c8853a","tid":1631161,"uid":52566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:53:55.000Z","msg":"聽日一撚定要夜晚18區開花<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629580</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0bc30669e1f7eda7f6d771774aa00969144542de","tid":1631161,"uid":112124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"我唔撚想輸啊"},{"pid":"a22bb8afd7358076fd8ffc54dc846020183ba810","tid":1631161,"uid":112124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:55:05.000Z","msg":"堅持左四個月啦，因為咁樣輸 我覺得好撚唔抵啊"},{"pid":"5bea1cfb7b5e0b0c700eaba4abb51903485cbfd3","tid":1631161,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T14:56:13.000Z","msg":"冇路 7.7 <br />\n結界師好波<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「極重要」《三份英國外交及國會報告》：